'''Friedel-Crafts reaction'''
#{{chemistry}} a [[substitution reaction]] in which an [[alkyl]] or [[acyl]] [[functional group]] replaces a [[hydrogen]] [[atom]] of an [[aromatic]] [[nucleus]]; it is [[catalyzed]] by [[aluminium chloride]]
